{"tid":2228461,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"為反送中運動寫左一首歌, 獻比自己, 亦獻比所有手足 (包括已與我們隔絕的手足)","createTime":"2020-10-03T14:52:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T18:34:02.000Z","uid":289694,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5324db0b306c3f15c3de38f8f4437fd0f78786f9","tid":2228461,"uid":289694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T14:52:25.000Z","msg":"[url]file:///C:/Users/user/Desktop/WhatsApp%20Audio%202020-09-24%20at%2011.04.22%20PM.mp4[/url]<br />\n<br />\n一息尚存, 抗爭到底<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"989945b02eb50258bb2aba14302a0dde037701eb","tid":2228461,"uid":231583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T14:54:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"87508b07d32674140c82fbfea072ea81cb547dde","tid":2228461,"uid":289694,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T14:54:28.000Z","msg":"MP3:<br />\n<br />\nfile:///C:/Users/user/Desktop/WhatsApp%20Audio%202020-09-24%20at%2011.04.22%20PM.mp3"},{"pid":"2fdefa57ae93add9f91b5606c9444af358549964","tid":2228461,"uid":289694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T14:57:07.000Z","msg":"歌詞:<br />\n<br />\n重光這遠景    埋藏你我腦海裡<br />\n無分彼此的角色  掀起革命<br />\n流亡他鄉於遠方  盼望你我再相見<br />\n願這終點烏托邦 一起建造<br />\n<br />\n無懼奮勇再踏前      初心不改變<br />\n榮光響起整片天 記載今天<br />\n誰沒試過作決定   即使得一次<br />\n沉澱過這鬥意   戰勝風雨<br />\n<br />\n無數個夜晚反抗      只因心堅決<br />\n群眾聲討於四方  走千遍<br />\n浩浩蕩蕩這都市         漆黑星火裡<br />\n吶喊聲中不變遷  走多遠<br />\n<br />\n就算偶爾也困倦   仍未現曙光<br />\n但這一刻捉緊你雙手<br />\n未來見"},{"pid":"447599edaf93544c6157f6acb54f32a94b9629a0","tid":2228461,"uid":289694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"989945b02eb50258bb2aba14302a0dde037701eb","tid":2228461,"uid":231583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T14:54:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T14:58:23.000Z","msg":"試下用電腦開？<img src=\"/assets/face